responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "A8AF51D543CE7C9BCE9F6F946FA17822", "The best we can hope to do is stem the flow of goblins into the ruins. I have a hunch that they\'re getting in through the lower ruins. We\'ve found tunnels in the sunken sections of the city that lead far out into the hills; We report them, Kina and her goons patch \'em up. Things quiet down for a while.")
